summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6253 for the improvement of Southwest Webster Street from 24th Ave. Southwest to 28th Ave. Southwest; and certain other streets, avenues, alley and easements; by constructing sanitary sewers and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 90364, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
